<left>
Arrays are a useful way of storing data.
A simple (or indexed) array can be declared with one of
the following:

<bigreen>declare -a ARRAY<clear>
or
<bigreen>ARRAY=( 'value1' 'value2' 'value3' )<clear>
or
<bigreen>ARRAY[0]='value1'<clear>
</left>
